{"tid":1889944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"之鋒：時代雜誌奇文：港人要求封關只因仇中？？？","createTime":"2020-02-21T01:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T10:49:43.000Z","uid":78047,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"558ea6e7f5a79d8914f037d1e80f50cd90a8e80d","tid":1889944,"uid":78047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T01:41:30.000Z","msg":"睇完之鋒個post，上網搵到篇文作者個Twitter：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/laignee/status/1230412251351306240?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flaignee%2Fstatus%2F1230412251351306240%3Fs%3D19&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqFyHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=4dd0c7e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flaignee%2Fstatus%2F1230412251351306240%3Fs%3D19&h=d90355b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/laignee/status/1230412251351306240?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n之鋒原post：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/2804235096335647/?sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200976479994868%2Fposts%2F2804235096335647%2F%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqFyHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=23ca1869\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/2804235096335647/?sfnsn=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n【時代雜誌奇文：港人要求封關只因仇中？？？】<br />\n<br />\n美國《時代雜誌》昨日刊登一篇奇文，全文不提香港口罩供應短缺、前線醫護防疫裝備荒謬地只剩一個月、香港隔離政策猶如「無牙老虎」、鄰近省市廣東省已經淪為第二大疫區、大陸逾80省市已經先過香港實施「封城」⋯⋯直接一口咬定香港人要求全面封關的理由就是「仇中」。<br />\n<br />\n自武漢肺炎爆發以來，香港政府每樣措施都荒腔走板，香港人在寒風中徹夜排隊仍然「一罩難求」，在極度絕望無助、眼見政府無能、上萬人流每日過關的情況下，要求全面封關根本是非常合理的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n奇就奇在，《時代雜誌》的記者明顯抱有成見地先入為主，因全文即使訪問了支持全面封關的港大感染及傳染病中心總監何柏良，卻竟然沒有提到任何支持封關的理由，只是單純引用一句「恐懼比疫情嚴重（Panic is spreading faster than the virus）」，便草草作結。<br />\n<br />\n其實該記者只要離開太古坊，到香港普羅大眾所生活的社區感受民情，便會發現支持封關的市民根本是「黃藍不分」&mdash;&mdash; 因為政府一日不封關，檢疫工作變相由大陸關口推到大家屋企、店舖的門口，只要一有家人、員工、顧客出事，其惡果由小市民自己食哂，政府則拍拍屁股走人！<br />\n<br />\n這個道理，之前因「打邊爐家族」而出事的店主定必感受至深。政府一日未封關，試問連口罩都買不到的升斗小市民，如何有能力分辨哪個客人、哪位員工會有潛在風險？<br />\n<br />\n外國月亮從來不是特別圓，外媒記者有時亦會有成見，所以跟國際社會的工作更加顯得重要￼，剛在Twitter向外國人解釋了該文的盲點，希望各位幫忙Retweet：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1230282751154081792\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1230282751154081792&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqFyHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=23be7cb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1230282751154081792&h=faeca650\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1230282751154081792</a>"},{"pid":"7b48904ae50bc952b83959ae4912b2d01770010f","tid":1889944,"uid":297997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T01:55:52.000Z","msg":"收錢姐"},{"pid":"44fb9cbb85d4519cc430f97361bfaa7e094f8b6c","tid":1889944,"uid":137569,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T01:55:58.000Z","msg":"陳浩天都屌過times偏頗<br />\n但係兒登俾人屌佢屌times<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec97d8561c8cb4ae48ed88d8a67d13b5804fc28","tid":1889944,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"44fb9cbb85d4519cc430f97361bfaa7e094f8b6c","tid":1889944,"uid":137569,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T01:55:58.000Z","msg":"陳浩天都屌過times偏頗<br />\n但係兒登俾人屌佢屌times<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T01:56:56.000Z","msg":"一單還一單<br />\n同一個記者之前幾篇都好撐香港"},{"pid":"e22a2b26f7db0b6532ae79a1a7c2b3afb9cbba89","tid":1889944,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:02:00.000Z","msg":"條左膠八婆TWITTER 完全冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01547c4948c5299adc1045abdcf1b40100a4bf31","tid":1889944,"uid":131691,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"44fb9cbb85d4519cc430f97361bfaa7e094f8b6c","tid":1889944,"uid":137569,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T01:55:58.000Z","msg":"陳